```json
{
  "translations": [
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b1",
      "translation": "In the fourth quarter of 2020, we celebrated AIA's tenth anniversary of listing on the Hong Kong Stock Exchange. Looking back, AIA's listing set multiple records at the time and remains"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b2",
      "translation": "the largest initial public offering in the global insurance industry to date. I am honored and gratified to work alongside the members of the Board. AIA's"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b3",
      "translation": "business has continued to develop and expand during this period, becoming the world's largest life insurance company by market capitalization."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b5",
      "translation": "All non-executive directors of the Board are independent individuals with extensive governance and leadership experience in both public and private sectors. We work together"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b6",
      "translation": "with determination to maintain a corporate culture that adheres to the highest international corporate governance standards. We firmly believe that a deeply rooted corporate governance culture, combined with a sound risk"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b7",
      "translation": "management framework, is the foundation for sustainable development of every institution."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b8",
      "translation": "One of the Board's important responsibilities is to ensure a strong pipeline of leadership talent and to implement effective succession arrangements. We welcomed Mr. Lee Yuen Cheung on 1 June 2020"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b9",
      "translation": "to succeed the retiring Mr. Wong King Fai as Group Chief Executive Officer and President. On behalf of the Board, I wish to express my deep appreciation to Mr. Lee Yuen Cheung and his management team"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b10",
      "translation": "for their outstanding management capabilities in navigating an unprecedented environment and driving our business forward. We also sincerely thank Mr. Wong King Fai"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b11",
      "translation": "for his excellent leadership over the years and his significant contributions to AIA."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b12",
      "translation": "Environmental, social and governance issues are increasingly important to the world. We are committed to doing our utmost to help drive society towards a better future, and our environmental,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b13",
      "translation": "social and governance initiatives were again recognized in 2020. According to Sustainalytics' assessment, AIA ranked second among over 270 insurance companies,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b14",
      "translation": "demonstrating our excellent corporate governance strength and quality. In addition, we continued to receive the \"Prime\" Environmental, Social and Governance Corporate Rating from Institutional Shareholder Services"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b15",
      "translation": "Inc. (ISS), recognizing us as one of the best-performing companies in the industry for sustainable development."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b16",
      "translation": "We believe we need to take further steps in this regard to achieve better outcomes for our communities. This remains a priority shared by myself, the Board"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b17",
      "translation": "members, senior management team and all our employees."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b18",
      "translation": "Today, customer demand for AIA's products, services and high-quality advice has never been more pressing. Our strategy is built on strong structural growth drivers in Asia,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b19",
      "translation": "supported by multiple factors, including unprecedented wealth creation, rapidly expanding protection gaps, evolving consumer preferences,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b20",
      "translation": "digital technology proliferation, and market focus on long-term sustainable development. The Board is confident that AIA is well-positioned to capitalize on the significant"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b21",
      "translation": "opportunities presented in the region, providing financial security to customers and their families when they need it most, giving them peace of mind, while creating shared value for all stakeholders."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b22",
      "translation": "Finally, it is thanks to the trust of our customers and shareholders that AIA has demonstrated strong and sustained growth since our listing. On behalf of all Board members,"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b23",
      "translation": "I sincerely thank you for your continued support."
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b24",
      "translation": "Tse Sze Wing"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b25",
      "translation": "Independent Non-Executive Chairman"
    },
    {
      "block_id": "p11_b27",
      "translation": "Growth rates are presented at constant exchange rates, which management believes provides a clearer illustration of the year-on-year performance of the relevant business."
    }
  ]
}
```
